{"tid":2275053,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"美國大選預驚世預言","createTime":"2020-11-07T01:19:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-08T14:47:14.000Z","uid":80108,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"0cc3b9e5699b1e43bdc1299d9575891afc199032","tid":2275053,"uid":80108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T01:19:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5henJ2e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5henJ2e.jpg&h=8d3ce0f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國總統大選，牽動億萬人的心，美國時間11月3號，一則8月份做出的預測在網絡熱傳。<br />\n<br />\n經阿波羅網 (<a href=\"http://www.aboluowang.com/2020/1105/1520071.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.aboluowang.com%2F2020%2F1105%2F1520071.html&d=J7URIij%2BjV7QbFiEH5rjuNAAr5%2FwdiPol2qeWm%2BM8v8%3D&h=28bf5d34\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.aboluowang.com/2020/1105/1520071.html</a>)記者調查，這個預測確實是在2020年8月28號，由大陸網友做出的，預測內容令人很震驚。<br />\n<br />\n預測中這樣寫到：「我用轉盤得出的結論： 拜登得財團（49國）扶持，靠不光彩的手段，使川普選票流失，排名落後。戌月末拜登宣佈當選，亥月初被川普發起異議推翻選舉結果，拜登下台（有可能入獄）。」"},{"pid":"91f4980c70370d051d4e13c2de84c6533a00d61c","tid":2275053,"uid":156096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T01:28:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1ba636f5eebfeccab5527794aa0634bf86eb6bdb","tid":2275053,"uid":64967,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T01:30:21.000Z","msg":"唔好諗咁多啦 你當左膠流？"},{"pid":"97e34316dab35db55c82204fa10d7d980a35ea27","tid":2275053,"uid":185126,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T01:30:47.000Z","msg":"粵劇特朗普預言今日開始轉運<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d096f4228e9160dc9c1ce842d1baa6ca4318e4e1","tid":2275053,"uid":156096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T02:10:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1fd586600f3dce63a68b4a95a7fed1cc46cc9741","tid":2275053,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T02:14:39.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"d0